asset_contract.name: Dogs of Elon
asset_contract.description:
Fair Launch
Launch date will be revealed publically, each participating address can only claim up to 20 of the 10,000 Dogs of Elon. At the end of the presale
https://dogsofelon.io

The Dogs of Elon – An NFT for the moonshot trader.
DoE is our passion project! We worked to create a CryptoPunks alternative that represented us, the meme coin hodlers. We have all witnessed the power of the meme coin community and its strength which has universally defied experts.

In celebration of this we have created 10,000 unique NFTs featuring everybodies favourite K-9. Containing special sub collections with 30 Elons and 70 zombies Doges.

To ensure the safety of the community, we took the extra step to get our contracts audited by CertiK.

(How many other NFT projects are audited? Not many.)

NFT Staking
As a celebration of the strongest communities in crypto, the DoE NFTs can be staked to earn $wDOGE and $SHIBA for a short period, one week after launch.

assets.name: ♻  (xn--26h)
assets.description:
DecentraWeb is a decentralized implementation of the DNS base layer protocol on the Ethereum Blockchain.

DecentraNames are decentralized TLDs (top level domains) and subdomains that live on the Ethereum blockchain as NFT ERC-721s and are minted and registered through DecentraWeb.

Anyone can permissionessly create their own top level domain (TLD) and own it permanently on the Ethereum blockchain.

DecentraWeb is committed to taking back the internet, one layer at a time...

For more information, visit https://decentraweb.org

  * traits have unique rarities and can be used in other apps in the future

asset_contract.name: CryptoFoxes
asset_contract.description:
CryptoFoxes are the only NFTs minted with a slot machine on the Ethereum blockchain. They are 11,111 for sale on [www.cryptofoxes.io](https://cryptofoxes.io/). They are the second generation of our collection (see the V1 here). All the important details about the collection are on [www.cryptofoxes.io](https://cryptofoxes.io/).

All the assets are handcrafted, then the CryptoFoxes are generated with a Python script in 48x48 GIF and scaled to 480x480 and minted on a Smart Contract ERC721 on Ethereum Blockchain. Each one is unique and crafted with its properties. Some of them are super rare!

Follow our [Twitter](https://twitter.com/CryptoFoxesNFT) for the latest news and join our [Discord](https://discord.gg/3crJeNYssT) to chat with the community.

The Genesis collection is [here](https://opensea.io/collection/cryptofoxes-origin).

assets.name: Goat Society #2238
assets.description: THE GOAT SOCIETY IS A COLLECTION OF 10,000 UNIQUE NFTS MEANT TO UNITE DIFFERENT COMMUNITIES AND FANS OF THE REAL-LIFE GOATS -- THE GREATEST OF ALL TIMES.

asset_contract.name: Goat Society
asset_contract.description:
[OFFICIAL WEBSITE](https://goatsociety.io/)

[OFFICIAL TWITTER](https://twitter.com/goatsocietynft)

[OFFICIAL INSTAGRAM](https://www.instagram.com/goatsocietynft/)

[HONORARIES](https://opensea.io/collection/the-goat-society-honoraries)

The GOAT Society is a collection of 10,000 unique NFTs meant to unite the different communities and fans of the real-life GOATs—the Greatest of All Times.

The collection includes 9,000 generative goats and 1,000 unique hand-drawn goats. Each goat is stored as ERC-721 tokens on the Ethereum blockchain.

Each GOAT grants a membership to the Herd, our exclusive group of investors that hail from a diverse range of communities. Herd members will receive benefits like access to major events like sports games, academy awards, music festivals, conferences, and concerts.

[OFFICIAL TWITTER](https://twitter.com/goatsocietynft)

[OFFICIAL INSTAGRAM](https://www.instagram.com/goatsocietynft/)

[HONORARIES](https://opensea.io/collection/the-goat-society-honoraries)

The GOAT Society is a collection of 10,000 unique NFTs meant to unite the different communities and fans of the real-life GOATs—the Greatest of All Times.

The collection includes 9,000 generative goats and 1,000 unique hand-drawn goats. Each goat is stored as ERC-721 tokens on the Ethereum blockchain.

Each GOAT grants a membership to the Herd, our exclusive group of investors that hail from a diverse range of communities. Herd members will receive benefits like access to major events like sports games, academy awards, music festivals, conferences, and concerts.
collection.name: THE REAL GOAT SOCIETY

The Wicked Craniums are the pictorial representation of the 10,762 Craniums that belong to the island of Osseous.

**OWNER COUNT**: Currently, the owners statistic shown by Opensea is inaccurate for this collection. This is because ~1.6k owners have [staked](https://etherscan.io/address/0xa265bd2ba7e49bcc77cef4a7b05c7799ec8b8387) their ~4.3k Craniums!
